data.description: Located in North Hampton on The Peninsula Estates, this impressive Arthur Rutenberg designed home overlooks a pond and the championship Arnold Palmer designed golf course. Open floor plan featuring a formal dining room, custom cabinetry, large island, walk-in pantry, and granite countertops. Enjoy dinner under the stars in the huge screened lanai with plenty of room for entertaining and summer kitchen. North Hampton amenities include a Jr Olympic pool, clubhouse, tennis and pickle ball courts, soccer field, kayak launch in the Outpost.
